des:
Kamonk products help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart home device.
After connecting Alexa to your Kamonk products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Kamonk" app in android or iOS app market;
(2). Register one Kamonk account in our "Kamonk" app;
(3). You need to have some Kamonk devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Kamonk" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Kamonk" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, iOS or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Kamonk" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Kamonk", and you'll be navigated to "Kamonk" login page;
(9). Open “Kamonk“ App—— More Service —— Link with Verification Code —— copy the Code —— Put code into the login page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
